I have left word at every
single hospital across the state

254
00:11:23,249 --> 00:11:24,832
to try and get you transferred.

255
00:11:24,867 --> 00:11:29,637
I can't make any promises,
but I'll pull every favor I can.

256
00:11:29,672 --> 00:11:32,006
But I'll have to start over.

257
00:11:32,041 --> 00:11:33,508
Be an intern again.

258
00:11:33,543 --> 00:11:36,327
I-I'm a year away
from a real salary.

259
00:11:36,363 --> 00:11:38,540
I have student loans that
have been in deferment.

260
00:11:38,564 --> 00:11:41,015
This is my career.

261
00:11:41,050 --> 00:11:42,945
I know, and I've spoken
to every department head

262
00:11:42,969 --> 00:11:44,102
to try and keep you here.

263
00:11:44,137 --> 00:11:45,920
There just isn't room.

264
00:11:45,955 --> 00:11:47,972
Oh, my God.

265
00:11:49,443 --> 00:11:52,042
I took a year's lease
on my apartment.

266
00:11:52,078 --> 00:11:53,939
I'm gonna have to move
home with my parents.

267
00:11:53,963 --> 00:11:56,114
I'm-I'm sorry. I
need, I need to go.

268
00:12:00,053 --> 00:12:02,064
And just like that,

269
00:12:02,088 --> 00:12:03,749
good doctors sacrificed
for the bottom line.

270
00:12:03,773 --> 00:12:05,851
These residents are
still in their training.

271
00:12:05,875 --> 00:12:07,052
It's almost impossible for them

272
00:12:07,076 --> 00:12:08,587
to get reassigned
into a new program.

