00:12:08,611 --> 00:12:10,206
Even if they do
find a new hospital,

274
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:12,847
they might have to start
over from their intern year.

275
00:12:12,882 --> 00:12:16,517
I came up with some
of these OB interns

276
00:12:16,553 --> 00:12:18,603
from med school.

277
00:12:18,638 --> 00:12:21,872
These are good
doctors, good people.

278
00:12:21,908 --> 00:12:23,524
I can't let them go until I know

279
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:25,555
I've done everything
I can to stop this.

280
00:12:25,579 --> 00:12:27,072
Mary Lawson's
test results are back.

281
00:12:27,096 --> 00:12:28,913
Thank you.

282
00:12:29,983 --> 00:12:30,983
Huh.

