00:12:31,017 --> 00:12:32,966
Not the news you
were hoping for?

284
00:12:33,002 --> 00:12:35,236
I'm not convinced any
news would be sufficient

285
00:12:35,271 --> 00:12:36,737
for this family.

286
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,550
- You need backup?
- Not yet.

287
00:12:38,575 --> 00:12:41,041
But if they start trying
to kill each other.

288
00:12:41,077 --> 00:12:43,294
I'll stand by.

289
00:12:46,249 --> 00:12:49,066
Well, I just reviewed
Mary's test results,

290
00:12:49,102 --> 00:12:51,386
and I'm happy to report
that everything looks normal.

291
00:12:51,421 --> 00:12:53,182
So there's nothing
wrong with me?

292
00:12:53,206 --> 00:12:55,940
Well, your symptoms
are real, but the tests show

293
00:12:55,975 --> 00:12:58,087
that nothing is emergent,
so that's good news.

294
00:12:58,111 --> 00:12:59,572
See?

295
00:12:59,596 --> 00:13:01,078
I told you.

296
00:13:01,113 --> 00:13:03,848
Here. Drink this.

297
00:13:03,883 --> 00:13:05,232
It helps with your stress.

298
00:13:05,268 --> 00:13:07,852
She said Mary's
symptoms are real.

299
00:13:07,887 --> 00:13:10,572
You don't look good,
kiddo. Are you okay?

300
00:13:10,607 --> 00:13:12,601
Actually, I'm not
feeling that... that good.

301
00:13:12,625 --> 00:13:13,824
I...

302
